views.definition:

    queryid,
    query,
    plans,
    total_plan_time,

    mean_plan_time,

    calls,
    total_exec_time,
    min_exec_time,
    max_exec_time,

    rows,

    local_blks_hit,

   FROM pg_stat_statements(true) pg_stat_statements(userid, dbid, toplevel, queryid, query, plans, total_plan_time, min_plan_time, max_plan_time, mean_plan_time, stddev_plan_time, calls, total_exec_time, min_exec_time, max_exec_time, mean_exec_time, stddev_exec_time, rows, shared_blks_hit, shared_blks_read, shared_blks_dirtied, shared_blks_written, local_blks_hit, local_blks_read, local_blks_dirtied, local_blks_written, temp_blks_read, temp_blks_written, shared_blk_read_time, shared_blk_write_time, local_blk_read_time, local_blk_write_time, temp_blk_read_time, temp_blk_write_time, wal_records, wal_fpi, wal_bytes, jit_functions, jit_generation_time, jit_inlining_count, jit_inlining_time, jit_optimization_count, jit_optimization_time, jit_emission_count, jit_emission_time, jit_deform_count, jit_deform_time, stats_since, minmax_stats_since);

vw_dashboard_final
views.definition:
WITH ind AS (
         SELECT vw_indicadores_gerais.clinica_id,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.clinica_nome,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.cnpj,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.external_id,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.mes_ref_date,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.mes_ref,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.qtde_boletos,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.valor_total_emitido,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.valor_medio_boleto,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.taxa_inadimplencia
           FROM vw_indicadores_gerais
        ), parc AS (
         SELECT vw_parcelamentos.clinica_id,
            vw_parcelamentos.mes_ref,
            vw_parcelamentos.mes_ref_date,
            vw_parcelamentos.qtde_registros,
            vw_parcelamentos.media_parcelas_pond,
            vw_parcelamentos.max_parcelas_mes,
            vw_parcelamentos.norm_parcelas
           FROM vw_parcelamentos
        ), pag AS (
         SELECT vw_pagamentos.clinica_id,
            vw_pagamentos.mes_ref,
            vw_pagamentos.mes_ref_date,
            vw_pagamentos.taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
            vw_pagamentos.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
            vw_pagamentos.percentual_faixa_0_30,
            vw_pagamentos.percentual_faixa_31_60,
            vw_pagamentos.percentual_faixa_61_90,
            vw_pagamentos.percentual_faixa_90_plus
           FROM vw_pagamentos
        ), score AS (
         SELECT vw_score_credito.clinica_id,
            vw_score_credito.clinica_nome,
            vw_score_credito.cnpj,
            vw_score_credito.external_id,
            vw_score_credito.mes_ref,
            vw_score_credito.mes_ref_date,
            vw_score_credito.qtde_boletos,
            vw_score_credito.valor_total_emitido,
            vw_score_credito.valor_medio_boleto,
            vw_score_credito.taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
            vw_score_credito.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
            vw_score_credito.taxa_inadimplencia,
            vw_score_credito.qtde_registros,
            vw_score_credito.media_parcelas_pond,
            vw_score_credito.max_parcelas_mes,
            vw_score_credito.norm_parcelas,
            vw_score_credito.max_inadimplencia,
            vw_score_credito.max_valor_medio,
            vw_score_credito.norm_inadimplencia,
            vw_score_credito.norm_valor_medio,
            vw_score_credito.score_credito,
            vw_score_credito.score_mes_anterior,
            vw_score_credito.score_variacao_vs_m1,
            vw_score_credito.categoria_risco
           FROM vw_score_credito
        ), limite AS (
         SELECT cl.clinica_id,
            cl.limite_aprovado,
            cl.faturamento_base,
            cl.score_base,
            cl.aprovado_em,
            cl.aprovado_por,
            cl.observacao,
            row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY cl.clinica_id ORDER BY cl.aprovado_em DESC) AS rn
           FROM clinica_limite cl
        )
 SELECT s.clinica_id,
    s.clinica_nome,
    s.cnpj,
    s.external_id,
    s.mes_ref,
    s.mes_ref_date,
    i.qtde_boletos,
    i.valor_total_emitido,
    i.valor_medio_boleto,
    i.taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
    i.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
    i.taxa_inadimplencia,
    p.qtde_registros AS parc_qtde_registros,
    p.media_parcelas_pond AS parc_media_parcelas_pond,
    p.max_parcelas_mes AS parc_max_parcelas_mes,
    p.norm_parcelas AS parc_norm_parcelas,
    pg.taxa_pago_no_vencimento AS pag_taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
    pg.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias AS pag_tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
    pg.percentual_faixa_0_30,
    pg.percentual_faixa_31_60,
    pg.percentual_faixa_61_90,
    pg.percentual_faixa_90_plus,
    s.norm_inadimplencia,
    s.norm_parcelas AS score_norm_parcelas,
    s.norm_valor_medio,
    s.score_credito,
    s.score_mes_anterior,
    s.score_variacao_vs_m1,
    s.categoria_risco,
    l.limite_aprovado,
    l.faturamento_base,
    l.score_base,
    l.aprovado_em AS limite_aprovado_em,
    l.aprovado_por,
    l.observacao AS limite_observacao
   FROM ((((score s
     LEFT JOIN ind i ON (((i.clinica_id = s.clinica_id) AND (i.mes_ref = s.mes_ref))))
     LEFT JOIN parc p ON (((p.clinica_id = s.clinica_id) AND (p.mes_ref = s.mes_ref))))
     LEFT JOIN pag pg ON (((pg.clinica_id = s.clinica_id) AND (pg.mes_ref = s.mes_ref))))
     LEFT JOIN limite l ON (((l.clinica_id = s.clinica_id) AND (l.rn = 1))))
  ORDER BY s.clinica_nome, s.mes_ref_date;

views.name: vw_indicadores_gerais
views.definition:
WITH base_boletos AS (
         SELECT b_1.clinica_id,
            b_1.mes_ref,
            to_date(b_1.mes_ref, 'YYYY-MM'::text) AS mes_ref_date,
            b_1.qtde AS qtde_boletos,
            b_1.valor_total AS valor_total_emitido,
            b_1.created_at,
            row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY b_1.clinica_id, b_1.mes_ref ORDER BY b_1.created_at DESC) AS rn
           FROM boletos_emitidos b_1
        ), base_taxa_venc AS (
         SELECT t.clinica_id,
            t.mes_ref,
            to_date(t.mes_ref, 'YYYY-MM'::text) AS mes_ref_date,
            t.taxa AS taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
            t.created_at,
            row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY t.clinica_id, t.mes_ref ORDER BY t.created_at DESC) AS rn
           FROM taxa_pago_no_vencimento t
        ), base_tempo_pag AS (
         SELECT p.clinica_id,
            p.mes_ref,
            to_date(p.mes_ref, 'YYYY-MM'::text) AS mes_ref_date,
            p.dias AS tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
            p.created_at,
            row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY p.clinica_id, p.mes_ref ORDER BY p.created_at DESC) AS rn
           FROM tempo_medio_pagamento p
        ), base_inadimplencia AS (
         SELECT i.clinica_id,
            i.mes_ref,
            to_date(i.mes_ref, 'YYYY-MM'::text) AS mes_ref_date,
            i.taxa AS taxa_inadimplencia,
            i.created_at,
            row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY i.clinica_id, i.mes_ref ORDER BY i.created_at DESC) AS rn
           FROM inadimplencia i
        )
 SELECT c.id AS clinica_id,
    c.nome AS clinica_nome,
    c.cnpj,
    c.external_id,
    COALESCE(b.mes_ref_date, tv.mes_ref_date, tp.mes_ref_date, ina.mes_ref_date) AS mes_ref_date,
    to_char((COALESCE(b.mes_ref_date, tv.mes_ref_date, tp.mes_ref_date, ina.mes_ref_date))::timestamp with time zone, 'YYYY-MM'::text) AS mes_ref,
    b.qtde_boletos,
    b.valor_total_emitido,
        CASE
            WHEN (b.qtde_boletos > 0) THEN (b.valor_total_emitido / (b.qtde_boletos)::numeric)
            ELSE NULL::numeric
        END AS valor_medio_boleto,
    tv.taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
    tp.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
    ina.taxa_inadimplencia
   FROM ((((clinicas c
     LEFT JOIN base_boletos b ON (((b.clinica_id = c.id) AND (b.rn = 1))))
     LEFT JOIN base_taxa_venc tv ON (((tv.clinica_id = c.id) AND (tv.mes_ref = b.mes_ref) AND (tv.rn = 1))))
     LEFT JOIN base_tempo_pag tp ON (((tp.clinica_id = c.id) AND (tp.mes_ref = b.mes_ref) AND (tp.rn = 1))))
     LEFT JOIN base_inadimplencia ina ON (((ina.clinica_id = c.id) AND (ina.mes_ref = b.mes_ref) AND (ina.rn = 1))))
  WHERE (b.rn = 1)
  ORDER BY c.nome, COALESCE(b.mes_ref_date, tv.mes_ref_date, tp.mes_ref_date, ina.mes_ref_date);

views.name: vw_pagamentos
views.definition:
WITH base_taxa_venc AS (
         SELECT t.clinica_id,
            t.mes_ref,
            to_date(t.mes_ref, 'YYYY-MM'::text) AS mes_ref_date,
            t.taxa AS taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
            t.created_at,
            row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY t.clinica_id, t.mes_ref ORDER BY t.created_at DESC) AS rn
           FROM taxa_pago_no_vencimento t
        ), base_tempo_pag AS (
         SELECT p.clinica_id,
            p.mes_ref,
            to_date(p.mes_ref, 'YYYY-MM'::text) AS mes_ref_date,
            p.dias AS tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
            p.created_at,
            row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY p.clinica_id, p.mes_ref ORDER BY p.created_at DESC) AS rn
           FROM tempo_medio_pagamento p
        ), base_faixas AS (
         SELECT f.clinica_id,
            f.mes_ref,
            to_date(f.mes_ref, 'YYYY-MM'::text) AS mes_ref_date,
            f.faixa,
            f.qtde,
            f.percentual,
            f.created_at,
            row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY f.clinica_id, f.mes_ref ORDER BY f.created_at DESC) AS rn
           FROM taxa_atraso_faixa f
        ), pivot_faixas AS (
         SELECT base_faixas.clinica_id,
            base_faixas.mes_ref,
            base_faixas.mes_ref_date,
            max(
                CASE
                    WHEN ((base_faixas.faixa ~~* '%0%'::text) OR (base_faixas.faixa ~~* '%30%'::text)) THEN base_faixas.percentual
                    ELSE NULL::numeric
                END) AS percentual_faixa_0_30,
            max(
                CASE
                    WHEN ((base_faixas.faixa ~~* '%31%'::text) OR (base_faixas.faixa ~~* '%60%'::text)) THEN base_faixas.percentual
                    ELSE NULL::numeric
                END) AS percentual_faixa_31_60,
            max(
                CASE
                    WHEN ((base_faixas.faixa ~~* '%61%'::text) OR (base_faixas.faixa ~~* '%90%'::text)) THEN base_faixas.percentual
                    ELSE NULL::numeric
                END) AS percentual_faixa_61_90,
            max(
                CASE
                    WHEN ((base_faixas.faixa ~~* '%90%'::text) AND (base_faixas.faixa ~~* '%+'::text)) THEN base_faixas.percentual
                    ELSE NULL::numeric
                END) AS percentual_faixa_90_plus
           FROM base_faixas
          WHERE (base_faixas.rn = 1)
          GROUP BY base_faixas.clinica_id, base_faixas.mes_ref, base_faixas.mes_ref_date
        )
 SELECT COALESCE(tv.clinica_id, tp.clinica_id, pf.clinica_id) AS clinica_id,
    COALESCE(tv.mes_ref, tp.mes_ref, pf.mes_ref) AS mes_ref,
    COALESCE(tv.mes_ref_date, tp.mes_ref_date, pf.mes_ref_date) AS mes_ref_date,
    tv.taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
    tp.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
    pf.percentual_faixa_0_30,
    pf.percentual_faixa_31_60,
    pf.percentual_faixa_61_90,
    pf.percentual_faixa_90_plus
   FROM ((base_taxa_venc tv
     FULL JOIN base_tempo_pag tp ON (((tv.clinica_id = tp.clinica_id) AND (tv.mes_ref = tp.mes_ref))))
     FULL JOIN pivot_faixas pf ON (((pf.clinica_id = COALESCE(tv.clinica_id, tp.clinica_id)) AND (pf.mes_ref = COALESCE(tv.mes_ref, tp.mes_ref)))))
  ORDER BY COALESCE(tv.clinica_id, tp.clinica_id, pf.clinica_id), COALESCE(tv.mes_ref_date, tp.mes_ref_date, pf.mes_ref_date);

views.name: vw_parcelamentos
views.definition:
WITH base AS (
         SELECT p.clinica_id,
            p.mes_ref,
            to_date(p.mes_ref, 'YYYY-MM'::text) AS mes_ref_date,
            p.qtde_parcelas,
            p.qtde,
            p.percentual,
            p.created_at,
            row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY p.clinica_id, p.mes_ref ORDER BY p.created_at DESC) AS rn
           FROM parcelamentos_detalhe p
        ), agg AS (
         SELECT base.clinica_id,
            base.mes_ref,
            base.mes_ref_date,
            sum(base.qtde) AS qtde_registros,
                CASE
                    WHEN (sum(base.qtde) > 0) THEN (sum(((base.qtde)::numeric * (base.qtde_parcelas)::numeric)) / (sum(base.qtde))::numeric)
                    ELSE NULL::numeric
                END AS media_parcelas_pond,
            max(base.qtde_parcelas) AS max_parcelas_mes
           FROM base
          WHERE (base.rn = 1)
          GROUP BY base.clinica_id, base.mes_ref, base.mes_ref_date
        ), norm AS (
         SELECT a.clinica_id,
            a.mes_ref,
            a.mes_ref_date,
            a.qtde_registros,
            a.media_parcelas_pond,
            a.max_parcelas_mes,
                CASE
                    WHEN (a.max_parcelas_mes > 0) THEN GREATEST((0)::numeric, LEAST((1)::numeric, ((1)::numeric - (a.media_parcelas_pond / (a.max_parcelas_mes)::numeric))))
                    ELSE NULL::numeric
                END AS norm_parcelas
           FROM agg a
        )
 SELECT clinica_id,
    mes_ref,
    mes_ref_date,
    qtde_registros,
    media_parcelas_pond,
    max_parcelas_mes,
    norm_parcelas
   FROM norm
  ORDER BY clinica_id, mes_ref_date;

views.name: vw_score_credito
views.definition:
WITH ind AS (
         SELECT vw_indicadores_gerais.clinica_id,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.clinica_nome,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.cnpj,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.external_id,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.mes_ref_date,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.mes_ref,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.qtde_boletos,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.valor_total_emitido,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.valor_medio_boleto,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
            vw_indicadores_gerais.taxa_inadimplencia
           FROM vw_indicadores_gerais
        ), parc AS (
         SELECT vw_parcelamentos.clinica_id,
            vw_parcelamentos.mes_ref,
            vw_parcelamentos.mes_ref_date,
            vw_parcelamentos.qtde_registros,
            vw_parcelamentos.media_parcelas_pond,
            vw_parcelamentos.max_parcelas_mes,
            vw_parcelamentos.norm_parcelas
           FROM vw_parcelamentos
        ), global_max AS (
         SELECT max(ind.taxa_inadimplencia) AS max_inadimplencia,
            max(ind.valor_medio_boleto) AS max_valor_medio
           FROM ind
        ), base AS (
         SELECT i.clinica_id,
            i.clinica_nome,
            i.cnpj,
            i.external_id,
            i.mes_ref,
            i.mes_ref_date,
            i.qtde_boletos,
            i.valor_total_emitido,
            i.valor_medio_boleto,
            i.taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
            i.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
            i.taxa_inadimplencia,
            p.qtde_registros,
            p.media_parcelas_pond,
            p.max_parcelas_mes,
            p.norm_parcelas,
            gm.max_inadimplencia,
            gm.max_valor_medio
           FROM ((ind i
             LEFT JOIN parc p ON (((p.clinica_id = i.clinica_id) AND (p.mes_ref = i.mes_ref))))
             CROSS JOIN global_max gm)
        ), norm AS (
         SELECT base.clinica_id,
            base.clinica_nome,
            base.cnpj,
            base.external_id,
            base.mes_ref,
            base.mes_ref_date,
            base.qtde_boletos,
            base.valor_total_emitido,
            base.valor_medio_boleto,
            base.taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
            base.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
            base.taxa_inadimplencia,
            base.qtde_registros,
            base.media_parcelas_pond,
            base.max_parcelas_mes,
            base.norm_parcelas,
            base.max_inadimplencia,
            base.max_valor_medio,
                CASE
                    WHEN ((base.max_inadimplencia > (0)::numeric) AND (base.taxa_inadimplencia IS NOT NULL)) THEN GREATEST((0)::numeric, LEAST((1)::numeric, ((1)::numeric - (base.taxa_inadimplencia / base.max_inadimplencia))))
                    ELSE NULL::numeric
                END AS norm_inadimplencia,
                CASE
                    WHEN ((base.max_valor_medio > (0)::numeric) AND (base.valor_medio_boleto IS NOT NULL)) THEN GREATEST((0)::numeric, LEAST((1)::numeric, (base.valor_medio_boleto / base.max_valor_medio)))
                    ELSE NULL::numeric
                END AS norm_valor_medio
           FROM base
        ), score_calc AS (
         SELECT norm.clinica_id,
            norm.clinica_nome,
            norm.cnpj,
            norm.external_id,
            norm.mes_ref,
            norm.mes_ref_date,
            norm.qtde_boletos,
            norm.valor_total_emitido,
            norm.valor_medio_boleto,
            norm.taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
            norm.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
            norm.taxa_inadimplencia,
            norm.qtde_registros,
            norm.media_parcelas_pond,
            norm.max_parcelas_mes,
            norm.norm_parcelas,
            norm.max_inadimplencia,
            norm.max_valor_medio,
            norm.norm_inadimplencia,
            norm.norm_valor_medio,
            (((0.5 * norm.norm_inadimplencia) + (0.3 * norm.norm_parcelas)) + (0.2 * norm.norm_valor_medio)) AS score_credito
           FROM norm
        ), score_m1 AS (
         SELECT s1.clinica_id,
            s1.clinica_nome,
            s1.cnpj,
            s1.external_id,
            s1.mes_ref,
            s1.mes_ref_date,
            s1.qtde_boletos,
            s1.valor_total_emitido,
            s1.valor_medio_boleto,
            s1.taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
            s1.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
            s1.taxa_inadimplencia,
            s1.qtde_registros,
            s1.media_parcelas_pond,
            s1.max_parcelas_mes,
            s1.norm_parcelas,
            s1.max_inadimplencia,
            s1.max_valor_medio,
            s1.norm_inadimplencia,
            s1.norm_valor_medio,
            s1.score_credito,
            ( SELECT s2.score_credito
                   FROM score_calc s2
                  WHERE ((s2.clinica_id = s1.clinica_id) AND (s2.mes_ref_date = (s1.mes_ref_date - '1 mon'::interval)))
                 LIMIT 1) AS score_mes_anterior
           FROM score_calc s1
        ), final AS (
         SELECT score_m1.clinica_id,
            score_m1.clinica_nome,
            score_m1.cnpj,
            score_m1.external_id,
            score_m1.mes_ref,
            score_m1.mes_ref_date,
            score_m1.qtde_boletos,
            score_m1.valor_total_emitido,
            score_m1.valor_medio_boleto,
            score_m1.taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
            score_m1.tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
            score_m1.taxa_inadimplencia,
            score_m1.qtde_registros,
            score_m1.media_parcelas_pond,
            score_m1.max_parcelas_mes,
            score_m1.norm_parcelas,
            score_m1.max_inadimplencia,
            score_m1.max_valor_medio,
            score_m1.norm_inadimplencia,
            score_m1.norm_valor_medio,
            score_m1.score_credito,
            score_m1.score_mes_anterior,
            (score_m1.score_credito - score_m1.score_mes_anterior) AS score_variacao_vs_m1,
                CASE
                    WHEN (score_m1.score_credito >= 0.80) THEN 'A (Excelente)'::text
                    WHEN (score_m1.score_credito >= 0.60) THEN 'B (Bom)'::text
                    WHEN (score_m1.score_credito >= 0.45) THEN 'C (Regular)'::text
                    WHEN (score_m1.score_credito >= 0.30) THEN 'D (Ruim)'::text
                    ELSE 'E (Crtico)'::text
                END AS categoria_risco
           FROM score_m1
        )
 SELECT clinica_id,
    clinica_nome,
    cnpj,
    external_id,
    mes_ref,
    mes_ref_date,
    qtde_boletos,
    valor_total_emitido,
    valor_medio_boleto,
    taxa_pago_no_vencimento,
    tempo_medio_pagamento_dias,
    taxa_inadimplencia,
    qtde_registros,
    media_parcelas_pond,
    max_parcelas_mes,
    norm_parcelas,
    max_inadimplencia,
    max_valor_medio,
    norm_inadimplencia,
    norm_valor_medio,
    score_credito,
    score_mes_anterior,
    score_variacao_vs_m1,
    categoria_risco
   FROM final
  ORDER BY clinica_id, mes_ref_date;

views.name: decrypted_secrets
views.definition:
SELECT id,
    name,
    description,
    secret,
    convert_from(vault._crypto_aead_det_decrypt(message => decode(secret, 'base64'::text), additional => convert_to((id)::text, 'utf8'::name), key_id => (0)::bigint, context => '\x7067736f6469756d'::bytea, nonce => nonce), 'utf8'::name) AS decrypted_secret,
    key_id,
    nonce,
    created_at,
    updated_at
   FROM vault.secrets s;
